    <p>
        <em>60 Second Burger Run</em> is an exciting and colorful speed-running platformer where your main goal is to reach a closing burger shop within a strict 60-second time limit! You control a cheerful, chubby hero who loves tasty fast food, and you must guide him through a series of challenging stages as quickly as possible. The game tests your reaction time, precision jumping, and ability to quickly memorize paths to pass as many levels as you can before the timer hits zero.
